trans-unit.source: Specifies the file format of the image.
trans-unit.target: Anger filformatet för bilden.

trans-unit.source: Not inheritable.
trans-unit.target: Kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: The properties of the ImageFormat class indicate image formats such as bitmap (<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Bmp%2A>), enhanced metafile (<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Emf%2A>), and icon (<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Icon%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Egenskaperna för klassen ImageFormat visar bildformat, till exempel bitmapp (<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Bmp%2A>), EMF (<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Emf%2A>), och ikon (<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Icon%2A>).</xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Icon%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Emf%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Bmp%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can use the properties of the ImageFormat class to specify an image format when saving an image using the <xref:System.Drawing.Image.Save%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Du kan till exempel använda egenskaper i klassen ImageFormat för att ange ett bildformat när du sparar en bild med hjälp av den <xref:System.Drawing.Image.Save%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Drawing.Image.Save%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can compare two image formats by using the <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Equals%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Du kan jämföra två bildformat med hjälp av den <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Equals%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Equals%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat"></xref> class by using the specified <xref:System.Guid> structure.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat"> </xref> klassen med hjälp av den angivna <xref:System.Guid>struktur.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.source: Typically you use the static properties of the <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat> class to specify a particular format such as <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Png%2A>or <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Jpeg%2A>, rather than constructing a new <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat>.
trans-unit.target: Du använder vanligtvis de statiska egenskaperna för den <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat>klassen för att ange ett visst format, till exempel <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Png%2A>eller <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Jpeg%2A>, i stället för att skapa en ny <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat>.</xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat> </xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Jpeg%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Png%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat>
